====== Social Media ======

To increase visibility, Ubucon is present on social media. In 2016 the accounts are:

  * [[https://twitter.com/ubuconeurope|Twitter]]
  * [[https://www.facebook.com/Ubucon-Europe-1099898853356780/timeline/|Facebook]]
  * [[https://plus.google.com/102116228818057372011/posts|Google+]]


===== Access =====

Social media accounts are managed by [[user>svij]].

In past years, Social media posts were manually generated when the News section on the website was updated.